    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Seven of thirteen credibility factors assessed; six not assessed, consistent with MRL 2 requirements. All assessed factors meet or exceed required levels. Discretization error, output comparison, and model form factors demonstrate adequate predictive capability for the hemolysis QoI within the COU operating envelope. Use-error factor is noted as not-assessed in this package, with reference to a companion IEC 62366 human factors evaluation; however, no linked artifact is provided and no use-error scenarios have been exercised within the validation activities. Overall credibility evidence is judged sufficient for the MRL 2 regulatory decision at this time.",
